ygData.subject: Aqualung Sales
ygData.msgSnippet: sorry my friend but for 700 plat anyone can purchase 50 enduring breath potions i dont really see why anyone would pay that UNLESS as stated earlier we provide
ygData.messageBody:
sorry my friend but for 700 plat anyone can purchase 50 enduring breath potions
i dont really see why anyone would pay that UNLESS as stated earlier we provide
an upgrade to rebreather for a viable cost. i agree with an earlier post wherein
we gig anyone who wont purchase the aqualung but wants a rebreather and cut some
slack to those who purchase both. this isnt really a prob for me as im only in it
to equip my guild and have full backing from them. just an opinion and glad to hear
the level cap is going to get fixed. you wouldnt believe the amount of cash i wasted
of the guild treasury trying to raise my skill. well see you all in game.
Derkal Pentolite, Eme'ef Aitch Wizard, The Rathe
